summary: I decided to make a room with most of the stuff that u need in a house and decided that i didnt want to have to go through the process of making bookshelfs everytime i made a mod so i made this rooom with the stuff i normaly use in a mod and decided to share it with everyone.
descriptionHtml:
This MOd is also usefuk for new moders that dont know how too make the bookshelfs
asnd who are wanting to start moding

to save time i just duplicate the cell and it works perfectly fine

heres a list of all the stuff in this room

3 Bookshelfs
2 mannequins
5 weapon racks
secret door
Alchemy table
Enchantment Table
3 Angled Display cases
2 Small Angled Display Cases

in the world space iteeriors the editor id is UtilityRoom
